    "en": {
      "title": "Party leaders take four decisions at the meeting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Harsha De Silva, Member of Parliament of the United People's Party, said in a tweet that four major decisions were reached at the party leaders' meeting.",
        "Mr. Harsha de Silva stated in his twitter message that the four decisions are the resignation of the President and the Prime Minister, the appointment of the Speaker as Acting President for thirty days, the appointment of a member representing the Parliament as the President and the formation of an all-party government until an election is held."
      ],
